South African Government Spokesman Manyi Says Media Hostile to Government

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-06-21T05:35:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-21/south-african-government-spokesman-manyi-says-media-hostile-to-government.html
Jimmy Manyi, the South African
government’s spokesman, said the country’s media is hostile
toward the state and there is a need for more diversity in the
industry.  Manyi spoke in an interview with Johannesburg’s 702 Talk
Radio today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  